Gheyme Stew

## Ingredients:
-beef meat
-tomato paste
-onion
-split peas
-rose water
-black or dried lime
-seasoning 

## Instruction:
Firstly, you chop up the onion and roast it with your favorite oil. It is suggested to use healthy one like Ghee or Avocado oil. Then
you need to add choped beef to the onion and mix them well till their colour perfectly change. In this time, you add split peas and
tomato paste to the combination, letting them to mix well on the medium heat. Remmember that you shouldn't add seanoning specially salt
in this level as it make the meeet tissue hard.
...
